[Edit] I originally had my own revised help file for SbieIni.exe in this thread, but it's not really a good place to post it.<br>So, I've moved it to my Dropbox folder and have included a link to it, below.<br><br>There are also a number of other files there, for use with SbieIni.exe.<br>You should read the file in Notepad, to get an idea of what it will do, if you rename it with a .cmd extension.<br>For the most part, these files are intended as examples, to show how to do something.<br>In a couple of cases, you can use the file as a template and add your own commands to the file before running it.<br><br>IN ALL CASES: The .cmd file must be placed in the 'Program Files\Sandboxie' folder, in the same folder as SbieIni.exe, before it will run correctly. That's because the files do not include a Path to the SbieIni.exe file.<br><br>YOU MAY WANT TO USE RIGHT-CLICK &gt; SAVE LINK AS... , or SAVE TARGET AS... to download the file.<br>My expanded help file:<br>SbieIni command line parameters.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/SbieIni%20command%20line%20parameters.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... meters.txt</a><br>------<br>Other files:<br>Sbieini List all sections.cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20List%20all%20sections.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... ns.cmd.txt</a><br><br>Sbieini List and sort boxes.cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20List%20and%20sort%20boxes.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... es.cmd.txt</a><br><br>Sbieini Query list of settings from [UserSetting].cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20Query%20list%20of%20settings%20from%20%5BUserSetting%5D.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... 5D.cmd.txt</a><br><br>Sbieini Query settings from a specified [UserSetting].cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20Query%20settings%20from%20a%20specified%20%5BUserSetting%5D.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... 5D.cmd.txt</a><br><br>Sbieini UnApply a local template.cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20UnApply%20a%20local%20template.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... te.cmd.txt</a><br><br>SBieini Create Sandbox.cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/SBieini%20Create%20Sandbox.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... ox.cmd.txt</a><br><br>Sbieini Delete a RecoverFolder setting.cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20Delete%20a%20RecoverFolder%20setting.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... ng.cmd.txt</a><br><br>Sbieini Delete value from all UserSettings.cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20Delete%20value%20from%20all%20UserSettings.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... gs.cmd.txt</a><br><br>Sbieini Find UserSettings sections.cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20Find%20UserSettings%20sections.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... ns.cmd.txt</a><br><br>Sbieini Modify template settings in GlobalSettings.cmd.txt<br><a href="https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandboxie/Sbieini%20Modify%20template%20settings%20in%20GlobalSettings.cmd.txt" class="postlink">https://dl.dropbox.com/u/16046062/Sandb ... gs.cmd.txt</a><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.sandboxie.com/phpBB3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1376">Guest10</a> — Thu Nov 29, 2012 8:27 am</p><hr />
